        Values in this file are example values only.
        PUF example file of basic invoice to create a FA XML version 3 invoice. Corresponding invoice type in FA (3): KOR_ROZ.
        In applicable cases the corresponding FA XML element is mentioned in parenthesis. 
        
        This example is based on KSeF official example file no. 18 (not covering additional buyer(Podmiot3, Rola 3))
